A warm, nostalgic vintage-style illustration of a freshly baked birthday cake with lit candles sitting on a wooden table near an old desktop computer from the early 2000s, soft golden afternoon light streaming through a window casting long shadows, the cake decorated with swirls of orange frosting that echo the glow of the monitor screen, a cozy home office atmosphere with warm sepia and amber tones, scattered confetti on the desk, the scene evoking a sense of personal celebration and digital connection, painterly brushstrokes reminiscent of Norman Rockwell's domestic scenes but with a turn-of-the-millennium tech twist.
